Class AssemblerSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cloudgraph.store.lang.AssemblerSupport
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultAssembler, ParallelSubgraphTask

    public abstract class AssemblerSupport
extends java.lang.Object
    Default assembler functionality without any shared objects related to graph assembly, such that it is usable by parallel tasks.

    0.6.2
